import React,{useEffect,useState} from 'react' import {useHistory} from 'react-router-dom' import axios from 'axios' function Post() { const [result1,setresult1] = useState([]) let history=useHistory(); useEffect(() => { if(!localStorage.getItem('Token')) { history.push('./login') } FetchPost() }, []) window.onscroll = function(ev) { if ((window.innerHeight + window.scrollY) >= document.body.offsetHeight) { // you're at the bottom of the page FetchPost() } }; const FetchPost=(index=0)=>axios({method: 'get',url:'http://localhost:5000/getPost',data:{index:1}}).then(result=>{ setresult1(result.data); console.log(JSON.parse(localStorage.getItem('LogInUser'))._id) }); return ( <> { (result1.length!==0)?result1.map(val=>
{val.title}
{val.category}
{ val.userId }
{val.date} {val.time}
